{"title":"水乡掠影","authors":["李根宝"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":10,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"水乡掠影（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李根宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿海村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禾苗象翡翠般发亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺展成绿色海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中间有个狭长的岛屿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映辉着红瓦白墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，那是一列船队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航行在碧波万顷的海上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日照烟纱缭绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹水波荡漾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听：七洲五洋的汽笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛在耳边震响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的船队全速竞航吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这春潮上涨的绿海，驶向金秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"之港！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月葵花金黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸中怀抱骄阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头婷婷玉立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含笑依傍南墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着河边的村庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯文、聪慧、芬芳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这多象江南的姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学得一手传统锦绣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣出了公社风光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要知姑娘的手艺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还看这葵花形象——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它编成一圈圈彩色花边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给所有的村落都镶上镜框。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走近宅前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举步刚刚进庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鸡拍打翅膀；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芦苇伫立河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头凝神眺望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将身走近村宅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白鹅嘎嘎直嚷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬，来了个不熟之客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊动了众位老乡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！快乐地欢叫吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前的一群鸡鸭猪羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这金风送爽的秋天里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿秋色象蓝天一样明朗！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}